*Deluje* na nas smirenim i mirnim tonom. (It is affecting us with a calm and peaceful tone.)

Njegova reč je *delovala* na mene kao blagoslov. (His word acted on me like a blessing.)

On je *deluje* neodlučno. (He appears indecisive.)

Vreme *deluje* na nas i menja nas. (Time affects us and changes us.)

Ponovo *deluju* na njega kao da je lud. (They are acting on him again as if he were crazy.)